| ActivityPods | MongoDB, Redis | `activitypods`, `mongodb`, `redis` |
| n8n | PostgreSQL | `n8n`, `postgresql` |
| Pixelfed | PostgreSQL, Redis | `pixelfed`, `postgresql`, `redis` |
| Castopod | MySQL, Redis | `castopod`, `mysql`, `redis` |
